---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Mister Mortgage USA"
  description="Mister Mortgage USA Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. NMLS #2572035."
  lang="en"
  canonical="https://mistermortgageusa.com/privacy-policy"
  hasTicker={false}
>

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container"><div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: March 25, 2026</p>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--white);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px;">
      <div style="color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.85;font-size:.97rem;">

        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Mister Mortgage USA Inc. ("Company," "we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or engage our services.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and mailing address.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Financial Information:</strong> Income, employment status, credit score range, down payment amount, and property value estimates provided during pre-qualification inquiries.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on our website, collected via cookies and analytics tools.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages, inquiries, and correspondence you send us through forms or email.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Respond to your inquiries and provide mortgage consulting services.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Process pre-qualification requests and connect you with appropriate loan programs.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Send you information about our services, promotions, and updates (with your consent).</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Improve our website and services through analytics and usage data.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Comply with legal obligations and regulatory requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Lending Partners:</strong> With your consent, to process loan applications and match you with suitable programs.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third-party vendors who assist us in operating our website and business (e.g., email services, analytics).</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law or to protect our legal rights.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Access the personal information we hold about you.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Request deletion of your personal information (subject to legal obligations).</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Opt out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">6. Cookies</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">We use cookies to improve your browsing experience and remember your preferences. For more information, see our <a href="/cookie-policy" style="color:var(--red);">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family:'Raleway',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us:</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:.5rem;"><strong>Mister Mortgage USA Inc.</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">6030 Bird Rd, Miami, FL 33155</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:.5rem;">Phone: <a href="tel:+13056151515" style="color:var(--red);">(305) 615-1515</a></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Email: <a href="mailto:info@mistermortgageusa.com" style="color:var(--red);">info@mistermortgageusa.com</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
